    FPTS

    Use the fantasy points slider to exclude players outside the specified fantasy point range. Note that this could refer to average fantasy points per game or the RotoGrinders projections depending the page.

    PT/$

    Use the value slider to exlude players outside the specified value range. Player value is defined as (fpts / (salary / 1000)). A high point per dollar ratio indicates strong value, whereas a low point per dollar ratio indicates weak value.

    • (D) Doubtful, Disabled (MLB)
    • (G) Game Time Decison

    Projected Points are listed in green for Premium Members

    Actual Fantasy Points are listed in purple for all past games
